<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Bethlehem ah chieh hitiu ie,
 Chamna Lalpa hung pienna chu;
 I lunggil gobawm teu hawngin,
 Lal thak chibai va buk hitiu.

[V2]
 Kipak leh lawpin lasa'i tiu,
 Chamna Lalpa chuh chawian in;
 Hossana ti a kiko in,
 Chungnung penah lopi pen hen.

[V3]
 2. Michingte leh belampute,
 Chunglam aksi chun a pui zel;
 Bethlehem a Lal thak pieng chu,
 Lawpin gimlimte a pieu hi.

[V4]
 3. Van mipite lawpna la chun,
 Chungnungpen ah lopi henla;
 Leichunga mihingte kawmah,
 &quot;Chamna thu leng hen&quot; a tiu hi.

[V5]
 4. Khuolbuk chang lo in tawm mahleh,
 A lopina zuol zel ina;
 Lal cheng cheng sanga Lalpen leh,
 Khawvel Hukdampa ahi ie.

[V6]
 5. Tuhin kipak in zaila sa'n,
 Chamna Lalpa chu chawian in;
 A chawih-at na'n khawvel thawng hen,
 Lopi pen hen Halleluijah.</lyrics>
<title>Bethlehem Ah !</title>
<hymn_number>37</hymn_number>
</song>